    {
      "text": "Appetite For Adventure\nShape up your Nintendo GAME BOY with foot-stomping action. Eat your way to super strength and pound everything in your path. Pick on everyone lighter than you as you make your way through 15 enemy-filled stages. Find the secret temples and take on the bonus stage challenges of thumb wrestling, arm wrestling or tradtional sumo fighting. Remember, don't forget to eat your rice!",
